p: Samples were analyzed by mass-spectrometry coupled with reversed phase ultra-performance liquid chromatography (ACQUITY UPLC System; Waters, Milford, MA, USA) in the positive ionization mode on Q-TOF Maxis Impact II mass-spectrometer (Bruker Daltonik, Bremen, Germany) (UPLC–MS). The settings were as follows: ion polarity, positive; scan mode, MS; mass range, 50–1200 m/ z, and spectra rate, 2 Hz.
